                        <locus target="#3v"/>
                        <desc> Described by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9602Turaev">Boris Turaev</persName> as "ornaments"; probably unfinished (uncoloured) ornamental bands or exercises in
                           ornaments drawing. </desc>
                     </decoNote>

